<!-- Popover — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/overlays.md#popover -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Popover</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">2 variants · 3 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Floating panel anchored to a trigger. Used for inline editing, contextual filters, info popups (richer than tooltip — can contain interactive content).</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">default · bordered</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">ghost · floating</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 200-280px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 240-360px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">lg · 320-480px</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closed</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">opening</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">open</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closing</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Behavior:</strong> click / hover / focus trigger (declared per use) · NO focus trap (Tab freely in / out) · dismiss on outside click + escape + scroll outside. <strong>Anchor:</strong> below trigger by default; flips above if clipped.</div>
</div>
